name: Jack A' Booran
desc: You can discard 1 Zombie monster; Special Summon this card from your hand. During your opponent's Main Phase (Quick Effect): You can target 1 Zombie monster in either GY; Special Summon it to your field, then banish this face-up card until the End Phase, also banish the Summoned monster when it leaves the field. You can only use each effect of "Jack A' Booran" once per turn.
